   <taskbody>
      <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">To be able to lift the system two plinth panels needs
to be removed. Decide if the front and back panels or both side panels
should be removed. It is recommended to select either the width or
depth depending on what is largest.</p>
      </context>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Remove the two screws <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b> in the plinth corners.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <image href="../Images/Modular_Bottom_remove-plinth1_0000704735.svg"
                      scope="local"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Remove the plinth panel <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <image href="../Images/Modular_Bottom_remove-plinth2_0000704734.svg"
                      scope="local"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Remove the opposite panel in the same way.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <note class="- topic/note ">Remember to attach the panels after the system has been
fastened to the floor.</note>
            </info>
         </step>
      </steps>
